69 Positions 5.2

◈ New Dark Mode support for iOS 13+!

◈ Larger screen size support for iPhone X and above

◈ Various bug fixes and performance improvements including: individually unlocked positions now persist after app close, position sharing improvements, and more!

Enjoy the new update? Be sure to leave your feedback in the App Store so we can continue bringing more!
